{
  "id": "adv_main_02_10_05",
  "title": "東京編2章25話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_office_noon",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_05-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "……天動瑠依、父親との共謀説浮上……\nI-UNITY出場は辞退……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“Rui Tendo‚ conspiracy theory with her father emerges…”\n“Withdrawal from I-UNITY competition…”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_05-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "バンプロ元社長朝倉氏の横領事件に関与の疑い……\n資金を着服……！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“Suspected involvement in former Van Productions president Asakura’s embezzlement case…”\nEmbezzlement?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_05-stm001.m4a",
      "text": "汚れたアイドルはファンを裏切り続けていたのか？\n……そんな言い方って酷過ぎます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“Has the tainted idol been betraying her fans all this time?”\nWhat cruel language to use!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_05-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "どのニュースもTRINITYAiLEに対する\n非難一色だ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "All the news is full of accusations\nagainst TRINITYAiLE…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_05-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "こんなことある訳ありませんわ！\n全部デタラメです！　くだらないゴシップ記事ですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There’s no way it’s true!\nIt’s all lies! A stupid gossip article!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.0663947582,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_05-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "私もそう思う\n瑠依さんに限ってありえない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ I agree with you.\nRui would never do something like this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_05-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃん達は\n本当に出ないんでしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is TRINITYAiLE\nreally not going to compete?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_05-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "いや、まだそう決まった訳じゃない\n彼女達が気持ちを強く持ってくれていたら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ it’s not a done deal yet.\nIf the girls are standing strong…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_05-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "本人に直接確認――くそっ、電話は繋がらないか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll ask them directly… Darn it‚ I can’t go through to them by phone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.4712246735,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_05-stm002.m4a",
      "text": "みなさん！　テレビ観て下さい！\n姫野さんが会見を！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Guys! Look at the TV!\nMs. Himeno is holding a press conference!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.734863907,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hotelconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hotelconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 58.7982687949
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_unrest-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 59.0190474509
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hotelconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hotelconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 59.0190474509
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "このたびは、お忙しい中",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you for taking time out of your busy schedules",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.8190474509,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_camera-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 59.8190474509
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_camera-02.m4a",
          "delay": 547.6192157999975,
          "startTime": 60.3666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_camera-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1080.9525490999974,
          "startTime": 60.9
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "お集まりいただきありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "to join us today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.7666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_camera-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 61.4476192158
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "我々プレタポルテにおいて重大な過失がありました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We at Pret-A-Porter have been grossly negligent.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "それをいち早くお伝えするためこの場を設けた次第です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thus‚ we’ve taken this opportunity to inform you as soon as possible.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "記者A",
      "speakerNameEn": "Reporter",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "早速ですが、TRINITYAiLEが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is it true that TRINITYAiLE",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "記者A",
      "speakerNameEn": "Reporter",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "今回の祭典、I-UNITYの四回戦を辞退した",
      "translations": {
        "en": "has withdrawn from the fourth round",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "記者A",
      "speakerNameEn": "Reporter",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "という話があるのですが事実でしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "of the I-UNITY tournament?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.2,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_camera-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5266.66666669999,
          "startTime": 87.4666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_camera-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5766.66666669999,
          "startTime": 87.9666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "残念ながら事実です。先日逮捕された朝倉恭一氏から",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Unfortunately‚ it is. Rui Tendo received a portion of funds",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "天動瑠依は資金の一部を受け取っていました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "from the recently arrested Kyoichi Asakura.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "事務所は協議の末、社会的責任を取るべく",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After careful discussions‚ our agency has informed TRINITYAiLE",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "彼女達の祭典への出場辞退と契約解除を通達しました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "of their withdrawal from the tournament and the termination of their contracts.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_camera-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4266.6666667000045,
          "startTime": 104.2666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_camera-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4733.3333332999955,
          "startTime": 104.7333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_camera-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5133.333333300001,
          "startTime": 105.1333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_camera-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5599.9999999999945,
          "startTime": 105.6
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_office_noon",
      "startTime": 106.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_05-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "！？　契約解除！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Termination of their contracts?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_05-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そんな、祭典に出られない\nだけじゃないなんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "N-no way. They’re going beyond\njust removing them from the tournament.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_05-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "そんな……トリエルは……\n瑠依さん達はどうなってしまいますの！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Unbelievable. What will happen…\nto TRINITYAiLE… to Rui‚ Yu‚ and Sumire?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_05-stm003.m4a",
      "text": "あれほど欲しがっていたトリエルを\nこんなに簡単に切り捨てるなんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She wanted TRINITYAiLE so badly‚\nyet she’s discarding them like nothing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_contact-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 128.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_05-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "……天動さん達が姫野さんに\nプレタポルテに逆らったからだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s because they defied Ms. Himeno.\nThey defied Pret-A-Porter.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_05-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "いかに優れたパフォーマーでも、自分達の思い通りに\nならなければ、排除するってことなんだ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It means that no matter how talented the performer‚\nyou’ll be eliminated if you don’t go along with what they tell you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_05-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（こんなの、許せる訳がない）\n（俺は……俺に出来ることは……！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(This is unforgivable.)\n(What is it… that I can do?!)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_05-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "酷い！　こんなの酷過ぎますわ！\n瑠依さん達なら、きっとスリクスにだって勝って……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is terrible! Absolutely terrible!\nI’m certain TRINITYAiLE would’ve been able to beat IIIX!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hotelconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hotelconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 156.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hotelconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hotelconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 156.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "記者B",
